                </div>
                <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">
                    Understanding <span class="gradient-text">Disasters</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle animate-on-scroll">
                    Knowledge is crucial for effective disaster preparedness. Explore our educational resources about different types of natural disasters and how to prepare for them.
