        <div class="disaster-grid animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="disaster-card">
                <div class="disaster-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-water"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Floods</h3>
                <div class="disaster-content">
                    <p>Floods are among the most common and destructive natural disasters, affecting millions worldwide each year.</p>
                    <div class="disaster-tips">
                        <h4>Safety Tips:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Evacuate immediately when advised</li>
                            <li>Avoid walking or driving through floodwaters</li>
                            <li>Move to higher ground away from rivers and streams</li>
                            <li>Prepare an emergency kit in advance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="disaster-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-value">90%</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">of natural disasters involve flooding</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disaster-card">
                <div class="disaster-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-wind"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Typhoons & Hurricanes</h3>
                <div class="disaster-content">
                    <p>These powerful tropical cyclones bring destructive winds, storm surges, and heavy rainfall that can cause widespread damage.</p>
                    <div class="disaster-tips">
                        <h4>Safety Tips:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Board up windows and secure outdoor objects</li>
                            <li>Follow evacuation orders without delay</li>
                            <li>Stay away from windows during the storm</li>
                            <li>Have a battery-powered radio for updates</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="disaster-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-value">160+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">km/h winds in severe hurricanes</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disaster-card">
                <div class="disaster-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Wildfires</h3>
                <div class="disaster-content">
                    <p>Climate change has increased the frequency and intensity of wildfires, threatening communities and ecosystems.</p>
                    <div class="disaster-tips">
                        <h4>Safety Tips:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create defensible space around your home</li>
                            <li>Have an evacuation plan ready</li>
                            <li>Keep important documents in fire-resistant containers</li>
                            <li>Monitor air quality and use masks when needed</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="disaster-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-value">85%</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">of wildfires are caused by humans</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disaster-card">
                <div class="disaster-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-mountain"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Earthquakes</h3>
                <div class="disaster-content">
                    <p>Sudden earth movements can cause devastating damage to infrastructure and trigger secondary disasters like tsunamis.</p>
                    <div class="disaster-tips">
                        <h4>Safety Tips:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Drop, cover, and hold on during shaking</li>
                            <li>Stay away from windows and exterior walls</li>
                            <li>If outdoors, move to open areas away from buildings</li>
                            <li>Be prepared for aftershocks</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="disaster-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-value">500,000+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">earthquakes occur worldwide each year</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disaster-card">
                <div class="disaster-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-smog"></i>
                </div>
