                        <h4>Safety Tips:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Use N95 or appropriate respirator masks when outdoors</li>
                            <li>Create a clean air space in your home with air purifiers</li>
                            <li>Limit outdoor activities during peak pollution hours</li>
                            <li>Stay updated with air quality index readings</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="disaster-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-value">7M</span>
